imdb.plot outline: "Crazy About You" is the story of Camilo and Juancho, two simple family young men, who share the dream to become famous musicians. On their way to success the meet Daniela, a high class woman who dreams to become a star and make a living from music. When the two young men fall in love with Daniela, their friendship will end. They will fight for her love regardless of the consequences. Two friends joined by music and separated by a woman's love.
imdb.title: Loquito por ti
plot: "Crazy About You" is the story of Camilo and Juancho, two simple family young men, who share the dream to become famous musicians. On their way to success the meet Daniela, a high class woman who dreams to become a star and make a living from music. When the two young men fall in love with Daniela, their friendship will end. They will fight for her love regardless of the consequences. Two friends joined by music and separated by a woman's love.
